nodes.description: Check current disk space usage on the system.
nodes.agent_prompt: Execute a command to check the current disk space usage. Return the output. This command might be 'df -h' on Linux/macOS or 'Get-PSDrive C' in PowerShell on Windows. Ensure the output is captured and returned as a string.
